title: (x) NBC show "Journeyman" opening titles - Clicker {Jan E}
content:
I took some screen shots from the titles of the NBC show.  
Looked around, but can’t seem to find what it is.  
It looks like Ganymede, but I know it isn’t.  
Any ideas?

Sleepily,  
Who Ha
